{
  "stem": "2684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a chemical engineer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he took me-- sorry, my wife, the child, and me to his home in Highett, in Victoria, Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know a word of English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know I'm in Melbourne, but that was about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew nothing about Australia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he took me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I stayed there for three weeks until Hakoah find me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I started playing soccer there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from then on, started my Australian way of life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents was very upset about our German names, because of the German happenings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I came home from Dachau in '47-- actually, I sent this gentlemen, Miklaus, to look for Andras Fischer, or Bonde Fischer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he couldn't find it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he asked a gentlemen named Fishcer, had a poultry shop here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the sellers said, you want Forgacs Bonde.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I want Fischer Bonde.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was Fischer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He's Forgacs now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's how we changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when I came back, the name on the shop was already Forgacs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked my mother, what is this Forgacs business?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, while you were away, by deeds of which I have papers here, you are Jules Forgacs from now on, because we don't want to be known as Fischer anymore.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went to the authorities, whoever that section belonged to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by deeds, by law they changed their name to Fischer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never read Fischer anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And only my childhood friends here, with whom I went to school-- I have a couple of them who knows me as Fischer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my name is Forgacs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody knows me by Forgacs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they took me from Doctor Kolinger-- Hakoah.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
